I stand before you today, taking full responsibility for my actions. I plead guilty to the offense of speeding. 

I would like to briefly explain the circumstances surrounding the offense. I was driving my brand-new car and the temptation to test its speed was overwhelming. In retrospect, I realize the danger I posed to those around me, and I deeply regret my actions. 

