Secondly, I have ADHD, a condition that may have influenced my impulsive behavior on this occasion. I do not offer this as an excuse but rather as an explanation for my actions. I am committed to seeking the necessary assistance and guidance to manage this condition effectively in order to prevent any future incidents.

I also wish to express my sincere remorse for the harm I caused and my willingness to make amends. I am prepared to undertake any actions necessary to compensate for the dangers I posed to others and to prevent the recurrence of such irresponsible behavior. 

Finally, I want to highlight my commitment to personal growth and contributing positively to society. While this offense is a regrettable occurrence, it does not define me as an individual. I have learned from my mistakes and strive to be a responsible citizen in all aspects of my life. 

In conclusion, I stand before you today, fully aware of my guilt and ready to face the consequences of my actions. I ask for your leniency considering the mitigating factors mentioned above. I assure you that I will take the necessary steps to rectify my behavior and become a law-abiding citizen.

Thank you for your consideration.

